&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; b) PUT /properties/1234?lock
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; 409 Conflict
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; The former bears the question what the server should do when the
&gt;&gt;&gt; client does not make
